76 [140617223504576] INFO perfrun.launcher <> - the option was added --p-state-trigger: Specify the name of the trigger event for P-state data as <string>. The default trigger is CPU_CLK_UNHALTED.REF_TSC.
76 [140617223504576] INFO perfrun.launcher <> - the option was added --rdt-auto-rmid: Enable automatic Core pinning on RMIDs for RDT monitoring capabilities.
